ðŸ’¡ Union is similar to Inner Join
ðŸ’¡ Union is adding two tables with Similar data but Non-repeated rows(if match found)
ðŸ’¡ Union is used only when both tables has similar Column names
    For ex.
    Emp
    EmpID | Name  | Dept
    10001 | Name1 | Dept1
    10002 | Name2 | Dept2
    10003 | Name3 | Dept1

    Salary
    EmpID | Salary 
    10001 | 5k
    10002 | 10k
    10003 | 15k



